dc_title_s: Pierhead and Bulkhead Lines for the East, West and North Shores of Newark Bay, New Jersey
dc_description_s: The map depicts the pierhead & bulkhead lines in the vicinity of Newark Bay, submitted in a report to the Chief of Engineers, USA, Washington D.C. recommending an adoption of these lines. |Map was modified Sept. 13, 1913 by USA and adopted by Riparian Commissioners of NJ on October 23, 1913.
